        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crush the <strong>cardamom pod<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>open by squashing it with the side of a knife</p><p>Add the <strong>garam masala </strong>and <strong>crushed cardamom pod<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>to a large bowl<strong> </strong>with the <strong>ground turmeric</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> ginger & garlic paste </strong>and <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> to the bowl along with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>vegetable oil</strong> and stir everything together – this is your <strong>Keralan-style</strong> <strong>marinade</strong></p>",
